{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"伤哉！每个诽谤者，诋毁者，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他聚积财产, 而当作武器，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他以为他的财产，能使他不灭。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"绝不然，他必定要被投在毁灭坑中。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你怎能知道毁灭坑是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"是安拉的燃着的烈火。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"能升到人的心上。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们必定要被关在烈火中，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"吊在许多高柱子上。"}]}